#: ../../talk/index.rst:3
msgid "Talk"
msgstr "Talk"

#: ../../talk/index.rst:5
msgid ""
"Nextcloud Talk offers audio/video and text chat integrated in Nextcloud. It "
"is available as a web interface, desktop client, and mobile apps for Android"
" and iOS."
msgstr ""
"Nextcloud Talk bietet Audio-/Video- und Text-Chat, die in Nextcloud "
"integriert sind. Es ist als Webinterface, Desktop-Client und mobile Apps für"
" Android und iOS verfügbar."

#: ../../talk/index.rst:8
msgid ""
"You can find out more about Nextcloud Talk `on our website "
"<https://nextcloud.com/talk/>`_. Download the desktop and mobile clients "
"from `nextcloud.com/install <https://nextcloud.com/install/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Mehr über Nextcloud Talk erfahren Sie auf unserer Website "
"<https://nextcloud.com/talk/>`_. Die Desktop- und Mobilclients können Sie "
"unter <https://nextcloud.com/install/> herunterladen`_."
